fields.Title: PARTY / CUNO MAIN
fields.Description: CUNO'S main hub inside whirling and on the island. It's like KIM MAIN

fields.Dialogue Text: "We can take another look in the mini-tower, where the bed was." He sniffs. "Let's check out where he shot my gimp. Ballistics shit. You should know that, pig."

fields.Title: Drama: "The kid is admitting falsehood, sir..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The kid is admitting falsehood, sire. He just doesn't know.

fields.Title: Logic: "Does he have a little *crush* on Li..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Does he have a little *crush* on Lilienne?

fields.Dialogue Text: "Well, I have been partying a lot lately..."

fields.Dialogue Text: "Goddamnit..." He looks down, shaking his head. "Cuno can't believe you're making up shit about him. This needs to stop."

fields.Dialogue Text: "You ever been inside the ruined building?"

fields.Dialogue Text: "Except what?"

fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno doesn't want to talk about this shit." There is a moment of thoughtful silence. He almost looks behind him.

fields.Dialogue Text: "Do you think he did it?"

fields.Dialogue Text: "How do you think the questioning is going?"

fields.Title: You: ""So who's side are you on?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "So who's side are you on?"

fields.Dialogue Text: "A fucking giant stick insect..."

fields.Dialogue Text: "You gotta hit *Magnesolam*, when you get off the train, pig. I always hit it to get the mag back."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""You know... break shit, throw shit..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You know... break shit, throw shit into the sea, throw shit into the windows, throw shit at the seagulls."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""You bet, pig!" He appreciates your..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You bet, pig!" He appreciates your validation. "Cuno lives the life to the max. Lives every day to the mega. Cuno's in the *moment* like that."

fields.Title: You: ""I'm trying to get him to confess...""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm trying to get him to confess..."

fields.Dialogue Text: This is the extent of the boy's knowledge.

fields.Dialogue Text: "Small time shit. Got it."

fields.Dialogue Text: The *Train*. Speed-Train. Amphetamine Express.

fields.Title: You: ""You like Lilienne, don't you?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "You like Lilienne, don't you?"

fields.Dialogue Text: "Ah, Cuno's not into that hallucinogenic shit -- that's for pussies."

fields.Dialogue Text: "Thanks Cuno, but enough about Martinaise."

fields.Title: You: ""Cool.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cool."

fields.Dialogue Text: "Cool place. Lot's of shit to do there."

fields.Title: You: ""What can I put on him, to get him..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What can I put on him, to get him to confess?"

fields.Title: Suggestion: "Good one, Cuno. It doesn't have to..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Good one, Cuno. It doesn't have to hold in court. Just establish a line of sight and he'll do the rest himself.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""He's into some ancient warrior shi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "He's into some ancient warrior shit. Hate shit. Pressure cook him. Push it on him, like -- motive shit. Pig style."

fields.Title: Empathy: "Being put in the spotlight like thi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Being put in the spotlight like this makes him feel exposed, makes him lash out.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno's a pig now." He picks his to..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno's a pig now." He picks his tooth with a dirty fingernail.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Shoot," he says with a nod. "Cuno..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Shoot," he says with a nod. "Cuno knows this shithole better than anyone."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Totally, pig. Cuno's in the same s..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Totally, pig. Cuno's in the same shit every time he's coming off speed." His tone gets parental. "You need to *medicate* that shit."

fields.Title: You: ""Whose statue is it on the roundabo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Whose statue is it on the roundabout?"

fields.Title: You: ""Like what?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Like what?"

fields.Title: You: ""I want to buy the FALN pants.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I want to buy the FALN pants."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Good." He nods. "I think it's goin..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Good." He nods. "I think it's going really fucking well." He leans closer. "Just cut it with the punching shit, alright? Makes us look like we got nothing."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Well *I* don't," the kid says, poi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Well *I* don't," the kid says, pointing to himself with his thumb. "Cuno's got no time for this shit. He's a pig now."

fields.Title: You: ""We still need to get him back, but..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "We still need to get him back, but... yeah. We got our man."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Talk to Cuno.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Talk to Cuno."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno used to hang there sometimes...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno used to hang there sometimes. It's a real shit-hole. Everyone is old or a fucking drunk or dead, except..."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno's in the game. Let's fucking..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno's in the game. Let's fucking do this, pig." he whispers, excitedly.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Well. There's the gun," he says, s..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Well. There's the gun," he says, scratching his head... "Why you still haven't picked it up and used it against him is beyond Cuno."

fields.Title: Half Light: "Liar. He doesn't have the guts to c..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Liar. He doesn't have the guts to climb in there.

fields.Title: You: ""Cuno, I have couple of questions a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno, I have couple of questions about Martinaise."

fields.Title: You: ""Let's move!" [Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: "Let's move!" [Leave.]

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Okay, so, we've got the old fuck."..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay, so, we've got the old fuck." The kid whispers, his eyes bugging out of his skull with excitement.

fields.Title: You: ""What am I missing? What haven't I..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What am I missing? What haven't I done?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Locust city?" He swallows. "Cuno d..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Locust city?" He swallows. "Cuno dropped that art shit coz Cuno's fucking *poor* and has shit for brains."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""You better not make Cuno fucking *..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You better not make Cuno fucking *cry* about his art-shit, okay? Change the subject, Cuno doesn't do that shit no more. Fuck that shit, fuck *everything*."

fields.Title: Logic: "He was probably collecting tare or..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He was probably collecting tare or stealing stuff that wasn't nailed down.

fields.Title: You: ""It's okay, I like her too.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's okay, I like her too."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""What do you mean, what's going on?..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What do you mean, what's going on? This is good shit." He seems surprised. "You wouldn't believe the crap Cuno's getting from the trucks."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""If you wanna take a real blasto, g..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "If you wanna take a real blasto, go down the coast to the old church, where the speedfreaks hang."

fields.Title: You: ""Have you ever been there?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Have you ever been there?"

fields.Title: You: ""Anything you can tell me about the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Anything you can tell me about the boardwalk with the ruins and the fishmarket?"

fields.Title: You: ""What happened to your art thing?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What happened to your art thing?"

fields.Title: Cuno: "The kid nods, obviously relieved."
fields.Dialogue Text: The kid nods, obviously relieved.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Whose side's Cuno on?!" His tone g..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Whose side's Cuno on?!" His tone gets angry. "Cuno's on fucking Cuno's side, pig! This is beneath the Cuno. Don't talk to me about this playground bullshit. You're getting shit in Cuno's head."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Makes you proud to be a pig," the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Makes you proud to be a pig," the kid says. "Oink oink."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Fucking island is spooky as fuck...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Fucking island is spooky as fuck. Cuno never liked it here."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno ain't spoiling this shit for..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno ain't spoiling this shit for you." He gives you something akin to a wink. "You gotta climb in there yourself and check it out."

fields.Title: Empathy: "You know who isn't old, drunk, or d..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You know who isn't old, drunk, or dead? Lilienne.

fields.Title: Empathy: "Just don't ask him about it. Boys i..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Just don't ask him about it. Boys in that age can be quite sensitive about such matters.

fields.Title: You: ""I'm sorry, Cuno. I'll stop.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm sorry, Cuno. I'll stop."

fields.Title: You: ""I'm pretty sure it's of Filippe II..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm pretty sure it's of Filippe III the Squanderer, the greatest of Flippian kings of Revachol..."

fields.Title: You: ""Your secret is safe with me, Cuno...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Your secret is safe with me, Cuno." (Give him a wink.)

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno is present on the scene." He..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno is present on the scene." He looks around with his hands on his hips.

fields.Title: You: ""What have you gotten there?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What have you gotten there?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah, yeah..." He fidgets uncomfor..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, yeah..." He fidgets uncomfortably. "Of course Cuno's been there, but that was a long time ago and I was fucked. Been on the train for fucking days. Can't remember shit."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno's been everywhere, pig.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno's been everywhere, pig."

fields.Title: Composure: "That is a look of a man who knows h..."
fields.Dialogue Text: That is a look of a man who knows he'll be looking over his shoulder for the rest of his life.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yes, Cuno can see that. You got th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes, Cuno can see that. You got this. Think of like..." He rubs his nose. "... what *other* shit he's done too. Cuno can tell he's a killer."

fields.Title: Suggestion: "Sounds like the kid has a soft spot..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Sounds like the kid has a soft spot for Lilienne.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah?" He places his hands on the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah?" He places his hands on the hips, waiting for your question.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah, pig... yeah." He scratches h..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, pig... yeah." He scratches his head. "It's a... seafort. For... It's for defence, pig. Don't bore Cuno with this historic shit."

fields.Title: You: ""What's going on with the traffic j..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What's going on with the traffic jam?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""That toxic shit's behind Cuno now.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "That toxic shit's behind Cuno now."

fields.Title: Cuno: "He unzips his jacket again and pull..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He unzips his jacket again and pulls the pants from the plastic wrapping. "Here pig, we both FALN now. Performance Pigs. Let's try not to shit ourselves."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno's in the game. Let's fucking..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno's in the game. Let's fucking do this, pig." he whispers, excitedly.

fields.Title: Composure: "You hear that? He thinks you're ver..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You hear that? He thinks you're very close...

fields.Title: Rhetoric: "Apparently he has never formed an o..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Apparently he has never formed an opinion on the matter and isn't going to do so on the fly either.

fields.Title: You: ""About Martinaise...""
fields.Dialogue Text: "About Martinaise..."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Oh, pig..." A clever smile runs ac..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Oh, pig..." A clever smile runs across his face. "Cuno's done with that shit. Cuno's a pig now. Living the pig-life. That reaver shit's behind him."

fields.Title: You: ""What did *you* do there?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What did *you* do there?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Also, the gun." The scratches his..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Also, the gun." The scratches his head. "Why you still haven't picked it up and used it against him is beyond Cuno."

fields.Title: Empathy: "A truly rare moment of self pity."
fields.Dialogue Text: A truly rare moment of self pity.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""What fucking secret?! You gotta st..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What fucking secret?! You gotta stop this shit with me!" He's trying to control himself. "Cuno's a pig. We're partners now. You got to be professional with the Cuno. Talk sense to him."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Uh..." He looks confused. "Well yo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Uh..." He looks confused. "Well you know, pig... Shit's fucked. And like... Cuno's got no time for this small time shit. Cuno's got *enterprises* to run."

fields.Title: You: ""No, it's more than that. It's like..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "No, it's more than that. It's like the city is speaking to me."

fields.Title: You: ""What are your thoughts on the stri..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What are your thoughts on the strike?"

fields.Title: You: ""No, I don't think it's actually dr..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "No, I don't think it's actually drug related..."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Wha-what?!" His face turns almost..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Wha-what?!" His face turns almost as red as his hair. "Are you fucking crazy, pig?! Cuno doesn't give two shits about that bird. Why do you even...?"

fields.Title: Cuno: "He nods in agreement."
fields.Dialogue Text: He nods in agreement.

fields.Title: You: ""Where is Cunoesse?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Where is Cunoesse?"

fields.Title: Cuno: "A crooked little smile. "Oh fuck, h..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A crooked little smile. "Oh fuck, he's practically dyin' to big up how he did it. Just get him to cough it up. Cuno's got your back."

fields.Title: You: ""I'm slapping myself to get ideas!""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm slapping myself to get ideas!"

fields.Title: You: ""Okay, let's do this." [Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay, let's do this." [Leave.]

fields.Title: Drama: "Good. Talk to him, demonstratively..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Good. Talk to him, demonstratively pick it up, then push it along with the other accusations. This is a good idea.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah, Cuno can see that," the kid..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, Cuno can see that," the kid says seriously. "So can fuckin' murderoonie here. You should stop -- it's weird as fuck."

fields.Title: Logic: "Of course -- why didn't *you* think..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Of course -- why didn't *you* think of it?! Motive shit. Pig style.

fields.Title: Cuno: "Cuno doesn't say anything. Stares o..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Cuno doesn't say anything. Stares out the window. You're on your own.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""You fuckin' better, pig!" His inde..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You fuckin' better, pig!" His index finger is pointed straight at you. "We're partners now. You got to be professional with the Cuno."

fields.Title: You: ""Okay. Cool.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay. Cool."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""We never did that ballistics shit..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "We never did that ballistics shit here." He sniffs. "Let's check out where he shot my gimp. You should know that shit, pig."

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "Something tells you this is going t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Something tells you this is going to be a rough ride.

fields.Title: Drama: "He tries to keep his voice casual a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He tries to keep his voice casual and businesslike, but it trembles ever so slightly.

fields.Title: You: ""I've had these weird shakes recent..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I've had these weird shakes recently. And something like... visions? Sounds familiar?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""If you know that history buff shit..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "If you know that history buff shit, then why are you fucking Cuno with this?" He shrugs. "Cuno's a pig now. Has important shit on his mind. Pig shit."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""She's okay," the kid suddenly spea..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "She's okay," the kid suddenly speaks with a high pitched squeak. "I mean... With all the fucking drunks and relics around, she's like the only one who isn't a walking shit hole. She's okay."

fields.Title: You: ""Mag?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Mag?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""It's Cuno's," he says without paus..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's Cuno's," he says without pause or hesitation.

fields.Dialogue Text: "Tell 'em Cuno sent you. They'll know what it means."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Except nothing." He shrugs. "That..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Except nothing." He shrugs. "That shit is behind Cuno. Keep your nose out of it."

fields.Title: You: ""Lilienne is nice though.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Lilienne is nice though."

fields.Title: You: ""What do you know about the village..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What do you know about the village southwest, across the canal?"

fields.Dialogue Text: "Magnesium, pig."

fields.Title: You: ""Yeah? What's in there?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah? What's in there?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno had some business ventures se..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno had some business ventures set up in the neighbourhood. Had money coming in... But not anymore." He punches an invisible target in the air. "Cuno's a straight-ass pig now."
